quran[564]{c,v,t}:
  78,1,Beebuuzaganya ku ki
  78,2,Ku kigambo e kinene
  78,3,Ekigambo kye baawukaniramu ddala
  78,4,"Ekyo ssi bwekiri, bajja kumanya"
  78,5,Oluvanyuma nedda bajja kumanyira ddala
  78,6,Abaffe tetwabafuula e nsi e kyaliiro
  78,7,N’ensozi ne tuzifuula enkondo (eziginyweza obutayuuga)
  78,8,Ne tubatonda mu ngeri bbiri (omukazi n’omusajja)
  78,9,Ne tufuula okwebaka kwa mmwe nga kiwummulo
  78,10,Ne tufuula ekiro ekyambalo ekibabikka (olw’enzikiza yaakyo)
  78,11,Ne tufuula emisana omunoonyezebwa eky’okubabeezaawo
  78,12,Ne tuzimba waggulu wa mmwe emyaliiro emigumu musanvu
  78,13,Ne tuteekawo ettaala (enjuba) eyaka
  78,14,Ne tussa okuva mu bire by’enkuba amazzi agafukumuka
  78,15,Tulyoke tumeze nago empeke n’ebimera (ebirala)
  78,16,N’amalimiro amasaakaativu
  78,17,Mazima olunaku lw’okulamula lwaweebwa e kiseera e kigere
  78,18,Olwo Lwe lunaku e ngombe lw'erifuuyibwa ne mujja nga muli bibinja
  78,19,N’eggulu ne liggulwawo ne libeerako e miryango
  78,20,N’ensozi nezikungunsibwa ne ziba nga ezitabangawo
  78,21,Mazima omuliro Jahannama weeguli gulinze
  78,22,Nga bwe buddo bw’abo abamawaggali eri Katonda
  78,23,Baakugubeeramu byeya na byeya
  78,24,Nga bali mu gwo tebagenda kufuna buweerero wadde ak'okunywa akaweweeza
  78,25,Okugyako olweje n’amasira Ag'olusaayisaayi
  78,26,Nga y’empeera ebasaanira
  78,27,Kubanga baali tebasuubira nti walibayo okubalibwa
  78,28,Ne balimbisa nnyo ebigambo byaffe
  78,29,"So ng’ate buli kintu twakikuuma mu bujjuvu, mu buwandiike"
  78,30,Kale mukombe ku kibabu ky'ebikolwa byammwe kubanga tetujja kubongera okugyako ebibonerezo
  78,31,Mazima abatya Katonda bajja kufuna okwesiima (okulimu buli kyonna kye baagala)
  78,32,Amalimiro n’emizabbibu
  78,33,N’abawala ab’amabeere amatutu
  78,34,N’amagiraasi agajjudde eby’okunywa
  78,35,Nga bali mu yo (e jjana) tebagenda kuwulira bigambo bya butaliimu wadde eby’obulimba
  78,36,"Nga y’empeera okuva eri omulezi wo, nga kuweebwa okumatiza"
  78,37,"Oyo nanyini Ggulu omusanvu n’ensi n’ebiri wakati wa byombi, oweekisa ekingi, tebalyetantala kwogeraganya naye"
  78,38,"Jiburilu ne ba malayika abalala ku lunaku lwe baliyimirira nga bali mu nnyiriri nga bonna tewali ayogera okugyako oyo yekka Katonda omusaasizi, gw’aliba akkiriza okwogera ate n'ayogera bituufu"
  78,39,Olwo lwe lunaku olw’amazima. Omuntu ayagala emirembe alwetegekere afune obuddo eri Katonda we
  78,40,"Mazima tubatiisizza ebibonerezo ebiri okumpi ennyo. Olunaku omuntu lw’aliraba ebyo emikono gye bye gyakola. Ku lunaku olwo omukaafiiri aligamba: ye nga zinsanze, singa nfuuse ettaka"
  79,1,Ndayira Malayika ezisikambula emyoyo gy’abajeemu mu bukambwe
  79,2,Era ndayira Malayika ezisowola emyoyo gy’abakkiriza obusowozi
  79,3,Era ndayira Malayika eziwugira mu bbanga oluwuga
  79,4,Era ndayira Malayika ezivuganya oluvuganya nga zitwala emyoyo gy’abakkiriza mu jjana
  79,5,Ne ndayira ne Malayika ezissa mu nkola ebiragiro (Byange)
  79,6,(Mukimanye nti ebitonde byonna bigenda kuzikirira) ku lunaku buli kintu kyonna lwe kirikankana nga engombe efuuyiddwa
  79,7,Luligobererwa olufuuwa olw'okubiri (olw'okuzuukira)
  79,8,E mitima gy’abatakkiriza ku lunaku olwo giribeera mu kutya
  79,9,Amaaso gaabwe nga makkakkamu
  79,10,"Bagamba (nga bajerega), nti \"Mazima ddala tulizzibwawo mu bulamu nga bwetulimu kati"
  79,11,Bwe tuliba tumaze okufuuka amagumba amamerengufu
  79,12,Bongerako ne bagamba nti (okwonno bwekiriba bwekityo) kuliba kudda kwa kufaafaaganirwa
  79,13,Mazima okuzuukira lugenda kubeera olukanga lumu lwokka
  79,14,Baligenda okulaba nga bali ku ngulu ku nsi
  79,15,Abaffe wamanya ku kyafaayo kya Nabbi Musa
  79,16,Awo Katonda we yakoowoolera Musa nga (Musa) ali mu lusenyi olutukuvu 'Tuwa
  79,17,N'amugamba nti genda eri Firaawo kubanga ye asusse mu bujeemu ne mu buwakanyi
  79,18,"Omugambe nti, Abaffe waalyetaaze okwetukuza (n'okkiriza mukama Katonda wo)"
  79,19,Ndyoke mbe nga nkulungamya eri Katonda wo obeere nga omutya
  79,20,(Nabbi Musa) n’alaga Firaawo obujulizi obwenkukunala
  79,21,(Firaawo) naalimbisa era n’ajeema
  79,22,Bwe yamala n'abikuba amabega era n’akola kaweefube w'okubirwanyisa
  79,23,"N’akungaanya (amagye ge, abakungu be, n’abalogo) n’alangirira"
  79,24,Ng’agamba nti nze Katonda wa mmwe owa waggulu
  79,25,Katonda n’amubonereza n’okumuzikiriza olw’ekisobyo ekyasembayo n’ekyasooka
  79,26,Mazima mu ekyo (eky’okuzikiriza Firaawo) mulimu eky’okulabirako eri oyo atya Katonda
  79,27,"Abaffe, mmwe be mweraba mwe musinga obuzibu okutonda okusinga e ggulu? Yalitonda nno"
  79,28,(Awamu n'obugevvu bwalyo) yaliwanika n'alitereeza
  79,29,Aleeta enzikiza yaalyo n’aggyayo ekitangaala kyalyo
  79,30,N’ensi oluvanyuma lwebyo yagyaliira
  79,31,Muyo mwennyini mweyajja amazzi gaayo namalundiro gaayo
  79,32,N’ensozi yazisimba n'azinyweeza
  79,33,(Ebyo yabikola) lwa kugasa mmwe n'ensolo za mmwe
  79,34,Akabenje akanene bwe kalijja (olwo lwe luliba olunaku lw'enkomerero)
  79,35,Olunaku lw’alijjukira omuntu ebyo byonna bye yakola
  79,36,Omuliro Jahiimu negulagibwa eri yenna alaba
  79,37,Oyo yenna eyasukka mu kujeema
  79,38,N’asukkulumya obulamu bw’ensi (ku bw'enkomerero)
  79,39,Mazima omuliro Jahiimu bwe buddo bwe
  79,40,Oyo aliba nga yatya okuyimirira mu maaso ga Mukama we (Katonda). N’aziyiza omwoyo gwe ku by’obwagazi
  79,41,"Mazima e jjana, bwe buddo bwe"
  79,42,"Bakubuuza gwe (Nabbi Muhammad) ebikwata ku lunaku lw’enkomerero, nti lulibaawo ddi"
  79,43,Wa gy'onoggya okulwogerako
  79,44,Omulezi wo Katonda yekka ya manyi ebirukwatako
  79,45,Mazima ggwe oli mutiisa eri oyo alutya
  79,46,Mazima bwe baliraba olunaku olwo balibanga abataatuula ku nsi okugyako ekiseera ky'olweggulo oba e kye nkya
  80,1,"(Nabbi Muhammad) azze emitaafu, n’akubayo amabega"
  80,2,Muzibe bw’amujjidde
  80,3,Ki ki ekikumanyisa ob'olyawo (muzibe oyo) aneetukuza
  80,4,Oba anaabuulirirwa okubuulira nekumugasa
  80,5,Oyo eyeegaggawaza nga yeematira
  80,6,Ate ggwe gwe weemalira
  80,7,Bw’ateetukuza kiki ekinaakubaako
  80,8,So ng’oyo akujjidde ng’ayanguwa
  80,9,Era ng’atya Katonda
  80,10,Ate ggwe gw’otofaako
  80,11,"Nedda si bwe kyandibadde, mazima yyo (Kur'ani) kya kwe buulirira"
  80,12,Aba ayagadde yeebuulirira nayo
  80,13,Eri mu biwandiiko eby’ekitiibwa ennyo
  80,14,"Ebigulumizibwa, ebitukuvu"
  80,15,Ebiri mu mikono gya Ba Malayika abawandiisi
  80,16,"Ab'ebitiibwa, abatukuvu"
  80,17,"Omuntu yakolimirwa, ki ki ddala ekimuwakanyisa Katonda"
  80,18,(Omuntu talaba) kintu ki Katonda mwe yamutonda
  80,19,Mu mazzi (e nkwaso) mwe yamutonda n'amugerera (byonna ebiri mutuukako)
  80,20,Oluvanyuma n’amwanguyiza ekkubo ly’okuzaalibwa
  80,21,Bw’amala n’amutta era n’aziikibwa mu kabbuli
  80,22,Oluvanyuma alimuzuukiza bwaliba ayagadde
  80,23,Wabula omuntu tatuukiriza ebyo Katonda by’amulagira okukola
  80,24,Omuntu ateekwa atunuulire by’alya (emitendera gye biyitamu)
  80,25,Mazima ffe tufuukirira amazzi olufukirira (olusaanidde)
  80,26,Ne tulyoka twasa ettaka olwasa (olusaanira ebimera)
  80,27,Olwo nno ne tumeza mu lyo e mpeke
  80,28,E mizabbibu n’ebimera e bizimba omubiri
  80,29,N’emizayituni n’emitende
  80,30,N’ennimiro ezisaakaatiddemu (e miti emiwanvu)
  80,31,N’ebibala n’omuddo oguliibwako e bisolo
  80,32,Bibagase n’ebisolo bya mmwe
  80,33,Naye okuboggola bwe kuliba kuzze
  80,34,Olunaku omuntu lwalidduka mugandawe
  80,35,"Ne maamawe, ne kitaawe"
  80,36,"Ne mukyalawe, n’abaanabe"
  80,37,Buli muntu ku lunaku olwo ajja kuba ku nsonga emukwatako yekka
  80,38,Ebyenyi ebimu ku lunaku olwo bigenda kuba byakaayakana
  80,39,"Nga biriko akamwenyumwenyu, nga bisanyufu"
  80,40,Ate ebyenyi ebirala bigenda kuba nga bigubye
  80,41,Nga ekizikiza kibibisse
  80,42,"Abo nno be baawakanya Katonda, aboonoonyi"
  81,1,Enjuba bw'erizingwako
  81,2,Nga n’emunyeenye zikunkumuse
  81,3,Era ensozi bwe zirikungunsibwa (ne zigibbwawo)
  81,4,Nga n’ebisolo ebyo mu maka nga tebikyafiibwako (newakubadde nga biriba mawako)
  81,5,N’ebisolo by’omu nsiko nabyo nga bikungaanyiziddwa
  81,6,Nga n’ennyanja zikuumiddwako omuliro (ne zibumbujja)
  81,7,"Nga n’emyoyo gigatiddwa buli egifaanagana nga giri wamu (Emirungi nga giri n’emirungi, e mibi nga giri n’emibi)"
  81,8,Era omwana omuwala eyaziikibwa nga mulamu bw'aliba abuuziddwa
  81,9,Kibi ki ekyamussa
  81,10,"Ebiwandiiko bwe biribeera nga bisasaanyiziddwa (nga buli kiwandiiko kituuka ku nnannyini kyo, omuli ebyo bye yakola ku nsi)"
  81,11,E ggulu bwe liriba liggyiddwawo
  81,12,Nga n’omuliro gukoleezeddwa
  81,13,Nga n’ejjana esembezeddwa
  81,14,Olwo omuntu alimanya ekyo kye yakola (kibe kirungi oba kibi)
  81,15,Ndayira e munyeenye ezibulawo
  81,16,Ezibula emisana ne zirabika ekiro
  81,17,Era ndayira ekiro bwe kiba nga kyolekedde okuggwaawo
  81,18,Era ndayira n’amakya g’obudde nga busaasaana
  81,19,Mazima yyo (Kur'ani) kigambo kya mubaka (Jiburilu) ow'ekitiibwa (ky’aggya eri Katonda n’akireetera Nabbi Muhammad)
  81,20,Oyo (Jiburilu) owaamaanyi era ow'ekitiibwa eri nnannyini Arishi
  81,21,Agonderwa (ba Malayika banne) eyo (mu ggulu) ng'ate mwesigwa
  81,22,Era munnammwe (Nabbi Muhammad) si mulalu
  81,23,Mazima ddala ye (Muhammad) yamulaba (Jiburilu) mu bweyolefu nga ajjudde obwengula
  81,24,Era tali (Nabbi Muhammad) ku bigambo ebyekwese (ebikwata ku bubaka obuva eri Katonda n'ebigambo by'omu ggulu) ayinza obutatuukiriza
  81,25,(Ebigambo bya Kur'ani Muhammad byayogera) si bigambo bya sitaani omukolimire
  81,26,Naye ddala mulaga wa
  81,27,Wabula Yo (Kur'ani) kyakubuulirira eri ebitonde byonna
  81,28,Eri oyo mu mmwe aba ayagadde okulungama
  81,29,Naye ate temujja kwagala okugyako nga Katonda Omulezi w’ebitonde ayagadde
  82,1,E ggulu bwe ririba lyeyasizzaamu
  82,2,N'emunyenye bwe ziriba nga zivudde waggulu ne zisaasaana
  82,3,N'ennyanja bwe ziriba nga ziwaguludde
  82,4,Ne Kabbuli bwe ziriba nga zifuukuddwa (abafu bonna ne bavaayo)
  82,5,Omuntu alimanya ebyo bye yakulembeza okukola ne bye yasembyayo
  82,6,Owange ggwe omuntu kale kiki ekyakugayaaza okukuggya ku muleziwo (Katonda) Omugabi
  82,7,Oyo eyakutonda n’akutereeza era n’akwenkanyankanya
  82,8,Mu kifaananyi kyonna kye yayagala mwe yakutondera
  82,9,"Nedda, wabula mulimbisa olunaku olw’okusasulwa (olw’enkomerero)"
  82,10,Mazima muliko abakuumi (Ba Malayika)
  82,11,Abeekitiibwa abawandiisi (abawandiika ebyo byonna ebikolebwa)
  82,12,Bamanyi ebyo byonna byemukola
  82,13,Mazima abakozi b’obulungi balibeera mu byengera
  82,14,Era mazima abakozi b’ebibi bagenda kubeera mu muliro oguyitibwa Jahiimu
  82,15,Bagenda kuguyingira ku lunaku olw’okusasulwa (olw'enkomerero)
  82,16,Tebagenda ku gwebulankanyako
  82,17,On'omanyira ku ki olunaku olw'okusasulwa (olw’enkomerero)
  82,18,Naye ddala on'omanyira ku ki olunaku olwokusasulwa (Katonda yakiddamu olwokuggumiza obukulu bw’olunaku olwo)
  82,19,Olunaku omwoyo lwe gutaliba na buyinza bugasa mwoyo mulala na kintu kyonna. N’ebiragiro ku lunaku olwo biriba bya Katonda yekka
  83,1,Okuzikirira kuli ku abo abakendeeza ebipimo
  83,2,"Abo bwe baba nga beebapimirwa, basaba ebipimo byabwe bijjuzibwe"
  83,3,"So nga bwe baba nga be balengera abalala, oba be bapima, bakendeeza (ebipimo)"
  83,4,Abaffe tebakakasa nti mazima ddala baakuzuukizibwa
  83,5,Ku lunaku oluzito (olw'enkomerero)
  83,6,Olunaku abantu lwe baliyimirira mu maaso g'omulezi w’ebitonde
  83,7,Mazima ddala ebiwandiiko by’emirimu gy’aboonoonyi biri mu Sijjiin
  83,8,Naye omanyi Sijjiin kye ki
  83,9,Ky’ekitabo ekiwandiikibwamu ebibi by’omuntu
  83,10,"Okuzikirira ku lunaku olwo, kulibeera ku abo abalimbisa"
  83,11,Abo abalimbisa olunaku lw’okusasulwa (olw’enkomerero)
  83,12,Tewali alimbisa lunaku olwo okugyako oyo asukka ensalo z’amateeka ga Katonda era omwonoonyi
  83,13,Bw’aba asomeddwa ebigambo byaffe (Kur'ani) agamba nti ebyo nfumo z’abaasooka
  83,14,"Nedda, ssi bwekiri; wabula bye baali bakola byetuuma ku mitima gyabwe"
  83,15,Mazima ddala abatakkiriza ku lunaku olwo baakuziyizibwa okulaba Omulezi waabwe (Katonda)
  83,16,Mazima ddala baakuyingira omuliro Jahiimu
  83,17,Oluvanyuma bagenda kugambibwa nti ekyo kye mwalimbisanga
  83,18,Mazima ddala ebiwandiiko by’abakozi b’obulungi biri mu Illiyyiina
  83,19,Naye omanyi Illiyyiina kye ki
  83,20,Ky’ekitabo ekiwandiikibwamu ebirungi by’omuntu
  83,21,Bakisemberera Ba malayika abali okumpi ne Katonda
  83,22,Mazima abakozi b’obulungi bagenda kubeera mu byengera
  83,23,Nga bali ku bitanda ebiwunde nga batunuulira ebintu ebibeetoolodde
  83,24,Essanyu eriribeera ku maaso gaabwe ligenda ku kulaga okwesiima kwe balibaamu
  83,25,Baligabulwanga omubisi (ogw’omu jjana) omusaanikire obulungi
  83,26,"(Olunaagunywangako) ng'owulira akawoowo ka misk. Ne mu kyo, abaagala okuvuganya mu kukola emirimu emirungi bavuganye"
  83,27,Omubisi ogwo gugenda kutabulwa mu Tasnim
  83,28,Tasnim nsulo erinywebwangako abalibeera okumpi ne Katonda
  83,29,Mazima abantu abo abaali abajeemu baalinga ku nsi nga basekerera abakkiriza
  83,30,Bwe baabayitangako nga babageyesa amaaso
  83,31,Ate nga bwe baddanga mu bantu baabwe nga beewaana
  83,32,Bwe baabalabangako nga bagamba nti mazima abo baabulira ddala
  83,33,Naye tebatumwanga kubeera nga bebalondoola emirimu gya bali
  83,34,Wabula olwaleero (olunaku lw'enkomerero) abo abakkiriza bajja kubeera nga basekerera abatakkiriza
  83,35,(Abakkiriza) nga bali ku bitanda ebiwunde nga babakeneka
  83,36,(Nga bwe bagamba nti) abaffe abatakkiriza basasuddwa bye baalinga bakola
  84,1,Eggulu bwe liryeyasaamu
  84,2,"Ne ligondera ekiragiro kya Mukama waalyo, era nga bwe kyandibadde"
  84,3,Ensi bw'eriseeteezebwa
  84,4,N'ewandula ebigirimu n'esigala nga njereere
  84,5,N'egondera ekiragiro kya mukama waayo era nga bwe kyandibadde
  84,6,Owange ggwe omuntu! Otakabana olutakabana (okukola e mirimu) ng'odda eri Katondawo. Era oli wakumusisinkana
  84,7,Kale nno omuntu aliweebwa ekitabokye mu mukonogwe ogwa ddyo
  84,8,Agenda kubalwa olubala olwangu
  84,9,Era adde eri banne nga musanyufu
  84,10,Naye oyo aliweebwa ekitabokye e mabega w'omugongogwe
  84,11,Agenda kukuba e biwoobe
  84,12,Yeesogge omuliro Sa-iira
  84,13,Kubanga yabeeranga (ku nsi) mu bantube nga musanyufu (mu kujeemera amateeka ga Mukama Katonda)
  84,14,Bambi! yalowooza nti tagenda kuzuukira
  84,15,"So nno, mazima Katondawe yalinga amulaba"
  84,16,Ndayira ekire ekimyufu (ekibaawo ng'enjuba yakagwa)
  84,17,Ne ndayira n'ekiro n'ebyo bye kikungaanya
  84,18,Era ndayira omwezi bwe guba gujjudde
  84,19,Mujja kukyusibwakyusibwa (mu mbeera za mmwe nga muva mu mbeera okudda ku ndala)
  84,20,Naye lwaki tebakkiriza
  84,21,Ne Kur'ani bwe basomerwa tebavunnama
  84,22,Wabula e nsonga ebagaana okuvunnama lwakuba nti abakafuuru balimbisa (Kur'ani)
  84,23,So nga Katonda amannyidde ddala bye bakweka (mu mitima gyabwe)
  84,24,Bawe amawulire nti bagenda kubeera mu bibonerezo ebiruma
  84,25,Okugyako abo abakkiriza ne bakola e mirimu e mirongoofu. Abo be bagenda okufuna e mpeera etakutukawo
  85,1,Ndayira e ggulu eririmu ebifo omutambulira e munyeenye (nga mwe muli e njuba n’omwezi)
  85,2,Era ndayira olunaku olwalagaanyisibwa (olunaku lw’enkomerero)
  85,3,Era ndayira oyo aliwa obujulizi n’oyo gwe balibuwaako (ku lunaku lw’enkomerero)
  85,4,Katonda yagoba mu kusaasirakwe abo abaasima agannya
  85,5,Gebaakumamu omuliro ogubumbujja
  85,6,Bwe baatuula awo ku mabbali waagwo
  85,7,Nga bo (bennyini) balaba buli kyonna kyebakola ku bakkiriza
  85,8,Tebaalina kye baali babavunaana okugyako okukkiriza Katonda oweekitiibwa atenderezebwa
  85,9,"Oyo, obufuzi bwe ggulu omusanvu n'ensi bwonna bubwe. Era Katonda alaba buli kintu"
  85,10,"Mazima abo abaawalagganya abakkiriza abasajja n’abakkiriza abakazi ate ne bateenenya, bakutuukibwako e bibonerezo by’omuliro Jahannama era balina e bibonerezo by’omuliro ogwokya ennyo"
  85,11,Mazima abo abakkiriza ne bakola e mirimu e mirungi bajja kufuna e jjana nga mukulukutira muyo emigga. Okwo nno kwe kwesiima okwannamaddala
  85,12,Mazima okukwata kwa Mukamaawo kwamaanyi nnyo
  85,13,Kubanga yye ye mutandisi wa buli kintu era yewookubizzaawo
  85,14,"Era musonyiyi nnyo, era abaagala nnyo"
  85,15,"Yye ye nannyini Arishi, Oweekitiibwa"
  85,16,Akola buli ky’aba ayagadde
  85,17,Wali owulidde ku byafaayo by’amagye
  85,18,Aga Firawo n’abantu ba Thamuud
  85,19,Wabula abo abatakkiriza bali mu kulimbisa
  85,20,So nga Katonda abeetoolodde
  85,21,Wabula yo Kur'ani (eyassibwa ku Nabbi Muhammad) ya kitiibwa
  85,22,Eri mu ggwandiikiro erikuumwa obutiribiri
  86,1,Ndayira e ggulu ne munyeenye ezirabika e kiro
  86,2,Naye omanyi e munyeenye ezirabika ekiro kye ki
  86,3,Z’emunyeenye ezaaka ennyo ekitangaala kyazo ne kiyita mu nzikiza ne kituuka ku nsi
  86,4,Buli muntu yenna aliko abakuumi (Ba Malayika)
  86,5,Kale nno omuntu yalibadde atunuulira kye yatondebwamu
  86,6,Yatondebwa ng’aggyibwa mu mazzi agasambattuka
  86,7,Nga gava wakati w’omugongo gw'omusajja n’amasaabiro g'omukazi
  86,8,Mazima ddala oyo (Katonda) asobolera ddala okumuzzaawo
  86,9,Ku lunaku ebyama byonna lwe biribikkulwa
  86,10,Omuntu tagenda kuba na maanyi gonna yadde omutaasa
  86,11,Era ndayira e ggulu ewava e nkuba etonnya nga e ddingana
  86,12,Ne ndayira n’ettaka eryeyasa olw’okumeza e bimera
  86,13,Mazima ddala yo (Kur'ani) kigambo ekyawula wakati w’amazima n’obulimba
  86,14,Kur'ani si ya lusaago
  86,15,Mazima abatakkiriza basala e nkwe
  86,16,Nange nenkola enteekateeka (zange)
  86,17,"Abatakkiriza balindirize, nange mbawadde akaseera katono"
  87,1,Tendereza erinnya ly’omulabiriziwo owa waggulu
  87,2,Oyo eyatonda n'atereeza
  87,3,Era eyateekateeka buli kintu n'akyenkanyankanya
  87,4,Era oyo ameza omuddo oguliibwa e bisolo
  87,5,Oluvanyuma agufuula omukalu
  87,6,Tujja kukusomesa (Kur'ani) obeere nga teweerabira
  87,7,Okugyako ebyo Katonda by’anaaba ayagadde okukwerabiza. Katonda y’amanyi ebyogerwa mu lwatu ne mu kyama
  87,8,Tujja kukwanguyiza amateeka gabeere mangu
  87,9,"Kale buulirira, okubuulirira bwe kuba nga kunaagasa"
  87,10,Anaaganyulwa oyo atya Katonda
  87,11,Omwonoonyi ajja ku kwesamba (okubuulirira okwo)
  87,12,Oyo alyesogga omuliro ogwamaanyi
  87,13,"Ng’amaze (okusonsekebwa mu muliro ogwo), tagenda kufa wadde okufuna obulamu (obwesiimisa)"
  87,14,Mazima yeesiimye omuntu e yeetukuza
  87,15,N’ayogera ku linnya ly’omuleziwe olwo nno n’asaala
  87,16,Wabula mmwe musukkulumya obulamu obw’ensi
  87,17,So nga obulamu obw'enkomerero bwe businga obulungi era bwe bwo kusigalawo
  87,18,Mazima bino biri mu biwandiiko ebyasooka
  87,19,Ebiwandiiko bya Ibrahim ne Musa
  88,1,Abaffe wali ofunye okunyumizibwa ku kibuutikira (eky’olunaku lw'enkomerero)
  88,2,Olunaku olwo ebyenyi bigenda kuba nga biswavu
  88,3,"Nga bitawaana, nga bikoowu"
  88,4,Nga byesonseka omuliro ogwengeredde
  88,5,Bigenda kunywesebwa ku luzzi olweseze
  88,6,(Abantu abo) tebagenda kubeera na kya kulya kyonna okugyako e miti egy’amaggwa
  88,7,Egitaliimu kiriisa wadde okuwonya e njala
  88,8,Ebyenyi e birala bigenda kubeera mu byengera
  88,9,Bigenda kusiima olw’okutakabana kwa byo
  88,10,Nga biri mu jjana ey’awaggulu
  88,11,Togenda kuwulira mu yo bigambo bya butaliimu
  88,12,Mu jjana mulimu e nsulo e zikulukuta
  88,13,Era nga mulimu ebitanda ebisitufu (Ebiwunde)
  88,14,N’ebikopo ebinywerwamu ebitegekeddwa
  88,15,N’emitto egisimbiddwa ennyiriri
  88,16,N’ebyaliiro nga byanjuluziddwa
  88,17,Abaffe tebatunuulira (olutunuulira olw’okuyiga) engamiya ngeri ki bwe yatondebwa
  88,18,N’eggulu nga bwe lyasitulwa
  88,19,N’ensozi engeri gye zaasimbwamu
  88,20,N’ensi engeri gye yaseetezebwamu
  88,21,Kale nno buulirira gwe (Nabbi Muhammad) kubanga oli mubuulirizi
  88,22,Toliiwo kubakaka
  88,23,Naye abo abanaava ku bigambobyo ne bajeema
  88,24,Katonda agenda okubabonereza e bibonerezo e bisinga okuba e bikakali
  88,25,Mazima ddala gyetuli y’eri obuddo bwabwe
  88,26,Oluvanyuma ddala okubalibwa kwabwe kuli ku ffe
  89,1,Ndayira e mambya
  89,2,N’ebiro e kkumi
  89,3,N’ebibiri bibiri n’ebyensusuuba
  89,4,N’ekiro bwekiba nga kitambula (nga kijja oba nga kivaawo)
  89,5,Abaffe mu kulayira kuno temuliimu kwebuulirira eri oyo alina amagezi
  89,6,Tewamanya ebyo Omuleziwo (Katonda) bye yatuusa ku bantu b'ekika kya A'adi
  89,7,Aba-Irama abawagguufu
  89,8,Tewatondebwangayo babafaanana mu nsi
  89,9,N’ebyo bye yatuusa ku ba Thamuud abaawukuulanga e njazi mu lusenyi
  89,10,N'ebyo bye yatuusa ku Firaawo nannyini nkondo
  89,11,Abo bonna (aboogeddwako) beewaggula kuno ku nsi
  89,12,Ne bayitiriza nnyo obwonoonefu
  89,13,Omuleziwo (Katonda) kye yava abafukirira e bibonerezo e by'enjawulo
  89,14,Mazima ddala Omuleziwo (Katonda) abalindiridde
  89,15,"Wabula omuntu, Omuleziwe (Katonda) bw'amugezesa n'amugabira e birungi, omuntu oyo agamba nti Katonda wange ampadde"
  89,16,Ku ludda olulala bw'aba amugezesezza n'amufundiza ebyenfunaye agamba nti omulezi wange (Katonda) anzikakkanyiza
  89,17,"Nedda, wabula temuyisa bulungi ba Mulekwa"
  89,18,Era temwekubiriza kuliisa banaku
  89,19,"Ate nga mulya emmaali ya ba Mulekwa, olulya olugimalawo"
  89,20,Era nga mwagala eby'enfuna okwagala okuyitiridde
  89,21,"Nedda eyo si y'endaba e ntuufu ey’ebintu, e nsi bwe ribeera nga ebetenteddwa"
  89,22,Omuleziwo n'ajja nga ne Ba Malayika basimbye ennyiriri
  89,23,"Era kwolwo o muliro Jahannama gulireetebwa, kwolwo nno omuntu alijjukira (bye yakola ku nsi) naye okujjukira kuno kugenda ku mugasaaki"
  89,24,"Agenda kugamba: zinsanze nze. Singa nategekera obulamu bwange buno"
  89,25,Olunaku olwo (Katonda) e bibonerezo by'agenda okubonereza nabyo tewali n'omu yali abibonerezzaako
  89,26,Era ensiba gyalisiba ku lunaku olwo tewali yali agisibyeko
  89,27,Owange ggwe omwoyo omutebenkevu (omuntu)
  89,28,Dda eri Omuleziwo ng'oli musanyufu era asiimiddwa
  89,29,Olwo nno oyingire mu baddu bange (abalongoofu)
  89,30,Era oyingire mu jjana yange
  90,1,Ndayira ekibuga kino (Makkah)
  90,2,Nga naawe (Muhammad) oli mutuuze mu kibuga kino
  90,3,Era ndayira omuzadde ne baazaala
  90,4,Mazima twakola omuntu nga lubeerera abeera mu kutawaana
  90,5,Alowooza nti tewali n’omu ayinza ku musobola
  90,6,Ng’agamba nti nsaasanyiza emmaali nyingi nnyo
  90,7,Alowooza nti tewali n’omu amulaba
  90,8,Tetwamuwa amaaso abiri
  90,9,N’olulimi n’emimwa ebiri
  90,10,Era ne tumulungamya okumanya amakubo abiri (ery'ekirungi n'ery'ekibi)
  90,11,Kale singa yabikozesa mu kuvvuunuka obizibu (bw'olunaku lw'enkomerero n'aba nga akozesa bye yafuna naafunamu e nkomerero)
  90,12,Abaffe obuzibu obumanyi (n'ekiyinza okubukuyambako)
  90,13,Kuta muddu
  90,14,Oba okuliisa mu kiseera eky’enjala
  90,15,"Mulekwa, owooluganda olw’okumpi"
  90,16,Oba omwavu lunkupe
  90,17,Ate era n’abeera mu abo abakkiriza. Ng’era balaamiragana obugumiikiriza nga bwe balaamiragana okusaasiragana
  90,18,Abo nno beebo abokubeera ku mukono ogwa ddyo
  90,19,Naye abo abawakanya e bigambo byaffe baakubeera ku mukono ogwa kkono
  90,20,Bagenda kubeera mu muliro omusaanikire
  91,1,Ndayira e njuba n’okwaka kwayo
  91,2,Era ndayira o mwezi bweguba nga gugoberedde e njuba (ng’egudde)
  91,3,Era ndayira obudde obw’emisana nga bwerudde enjuba
  91,4,Era ndayira ekiro bwe kiba nga kigibisse
  91,5,Era ndayira e ggulu n’eyalitonda
  91,6,Era ndayira e nsi n’oyo eyajaaliira
  91,7,Era ndayira omuntu n’eyamutonda
  91,8,N’amuwa okwawula wakati w’ekibi n’ekirungi
  91,9,Yeesiimye alongoosa omwoyogwe okuguggya mu bibi
  91,10,Aviiriddemu awo oyo agunnyika mu bibi
  91,11,"Abantu ba Thamuud, olw'obwonoonefu bwabwe baalimbisa (omubaka waabwe)"
  91,12,Asinga obwonoonefu mu bo bwe yeesowolayo (naafumita engamiya)
  91,13,Omubaka wa Katonda n’abagamba “muleke e ngamiya ya Katonda n’okunywa kwayo”
  91,14,Kyokka ne bamulimbisa ne bagifumita. Katonda omulabirizi waabwe kwe kubabuutikira olw’obwonoonefu bwabwe awatali n’omu kuwona
  91,15,Era tatya nkomerero y'ekyo (eky'okubazikiriza)
  92,1,Ndayira ekiro bwe kiba kibisse (e nsi)
  92,2,Ndayira n'obudde bwemisana bwe buba nga bwetadde
  92,3,Ndayira oyo eyatonda ekisajja n’ekikazi
  92,4,Mazima ddala okulafuubana kwa mmwe si kwe kumu
  92,5,"N'olwekyo, omuntu awaayo ekintu kyonna ng’atya Katonda"
  92,6,Nakkiriza e birungi. (ebiva mu kukkiriza Katonda)
  92,7,Tujja kumwanguyiza e kkubo erimutuusa eri obwangu
  92,8,Ate oyo akodowala ne yeegaggasa (ng’alowooza nti ebiri ewa Katonda tabyetaaga)
  92,9,N’alimbisa obubaka obwakkira ku Nabbi Muhammad
  92,10,Tujja kumwanguyiza okutuuka eri obuzibu
  92,11,N’obugaggabwe tebugenda kumugasa ng’ayingidde okuzikirira (olw’ebikolwa bye ebibi)
  92,12,Mazima kuli ku ffe okulungamya
  92,13,Era mazima ebikwata ku nkomerero ne nsi biri mu buyinza bwaffe
  92,14,Mbeekesa omuliro ogubumbujja
  92,15,Taliguyingira okugyako oyo omwonoonefu ennyo
  92,16,Oyo alimbisa (e bigambo bya Katonda) n'ayawukana (ku kugondera n'okukkiriza Katonda)
  92,17,"So nga oyo asinga okutya Katonda, ajja kugwesambisibwa"
  92,18,Oyo awaayo ku by'alina ng’anoonya okwetukuza eri Katonda (so si bandabe oba okwatiikirira)
  92,19,Nga tewali n'omu alina kiyinza ku musasulwa
  92,20,Wabula okunoonya okusiimwa ewa mukamaawe owa waggulu ennyo
  92,21,Mazima ddala ajja kusiima (ky’anaasasulwa)
  93,1,Ndayira ekiseera ky’a kalasa mayanzi
  93,2,Era ndayira e kiro bwekiba nga kikutte
  93,3,Omuleziwo Katonda takwabuliranga (gwe Nabbi Muhammad) era takukyawanga
  93,4,Era ddala e nkomerero y’ennungi gy’oli okusinga entandikwa
  93,5,Era ddala Omuleziwo ajja kukuwa naawe osiime
  93,6,Teyakusanga ng’oli mulekwa n'akulabirira
  93,7,Era teyakusanga nga tomanyi n’akulungamya
  93,8,Era teyakusanga nga oli mwavu n’akugaggawaza
  93,9,Kale nno mulekwa tomukaayuukiranga
  93,10,N’omuntu asaba tomuboggoleranga
  93,11,Ate era e kyengera kyonna Omuleziwo Katonda ky’abanga akuwadde kinyumyengako
  94,1,Tetwakwanjululiza ekifubakyo (eri obwa Nabbi n’okumanya ebigambo eby’amagezi)
  94,2,Ne tukuwewulira obuzito obwakuliko
  94,3,Obuzito obwo obwalibadde bukubendula omugongo
  94,4,Era ne tukuwa okwogerwako
  94,5,"(Kisaana kitegerekeke nti) mazima ddala buli awabeera obuzibu, wabaawo obwangu"
  94,6,Mazima ddala buli awabeera obuzibu wabaawo obwangu
  94,7,Bwoba nga omaze okukola emirimu (egikuyimirizaawo ku nsi) olwo nno yimirira (osinze Katondawo)
  94,8,"Era eri Omuleziwo Katonda, gy’oba oteeka e ssuubilyo lyonna"
  95,1,Ndayira ekibala ekiyitibwa Tiin n’ekibala ekiyitibwa Zaitun
  95,2,Era ndayira olusozi lw’e Sinai
  95,3,Nakino e kibuga (Makkah) eky’emirembe
  95,4,Mazima twakola omuntu mu kifaananyi e kisinga okuba ekirungi
  95,5,Ate oluvanyuma tumuzzaayo wansi mu ddaala erisembayo
  95,6,"Okugyako abo abakkiriza ne bakola e mirimu e mirungi, bagenda kufuna e mpeera etalina kkomo"
  95,7,Bwekiba bw'ekityo (ate gwe omuntu) olimbisa otya olunaku lw'enkomerero
  95,8,Tolaba nti Katonda ye Mulamuzi asinga okuba omwenkanya era owamazima
  96,1,Soma ng'otandika ne linnya lya mukamawo oyo eyatonda (buli kintu)
  96,2,Yatonda omuntu nga amuggya mu kisaayisaayi
  96,3,"Soma, kuba Omulezi wo (Katonda) ye mugabi asinga"
  96,4,Oyo eyayigiriza omuntu okuwandiika n'ekkalaamu
  96,5,Yayigiriza omuntu ebyo (omuntu) bye yali tamanyi
  96,6,"Nedda, mazima omuntu agenda neyewaggula"
  96,7,Olw’okweraba nti yeemalirira (olw’ebyo by’aba alina)
  96,8,Ng’ate Mazima ddala eri Omuleziwo (Katonda) y’eri obuddo
  96,9,Olabye omuntu agaana
  96,10,(Agaana) omuddu wa Katonda bw’aba ng'asaala
  96,11,Tolaba nti gwebagaana ky'akola kya bulungamu
  96,12,Oba bwaba alagidde abantu okutya Katonda
  96,13,Olaba oyo (agaana asaala) bw'alimbisa n'akyuka okuva ku mazima
  96,14,Abaffe tamanyi (oyo alimbisa) nti Mazima Katonda alaba ebyo (by’akola)
  96,15,Nedda bw’anaaba teyeekomyeko (ku bikolwa ebyo) tujja kumuwalula nga tumukutte ku kawompo
  96,16,Akawompo ako akajjudde obulimba n’obusobya
  96,17,Kale ayitanga abali mu kinywi kye (eky’obujeemu bamutaase)
  96,18,Naffe tujja kukoowoola ba Malayika abakambwe abakuumi b’omuliro (abatuusa ebibonerezo ku bajeemu)
  96,19,Nedda (Owange Nabbi Muhammad) togonderanga omuntu ng’oyo. Vunnama (ng'osinza) Katonda era weeyongere okusembera gy'ali
  97,1,Mazima ffe twassa Kur'ani mu kiro ekiyitibwa Layila-tul-kadri (e kiro ekyokugera era ekyekitiibwa)
  97,2,Ye nno omanyi Layila-tul-kadri kye ki
  97,3,Layila-tul-kadri kiro kirungi okusinga emyezi olukumi
  97,4,"Mu kiro ekyo, ba Mlayika bakka nga ne Jiburilu mwali ku lw’ekiragiro kya mukama waabwe (Katonda). Nga bajja na buli kiragiro"
  97,5,"Ekiro ekyo kya mirembe myereere, okutuusa obudde okukya"
  98,1,"Abajeemu mu bantu abaweebwa e kitabo, n'abo abagatta ebintu ebirala ku Katonda, tebaali baakuva ku nzikiriza yaabwe enkyamu okutuusa nga obunnyonnyofu bubajjidde"
  98,2,"Nga, ye Mubaka (Nabbi Muhammad) eyatumwa okuva ewa Katonda, nga asoma ekitabo ekitukuvu (Kur'ani)"
  98,3,Ekirimu amateeka amalambulukufu
  98,4,Era abantu abo abaweebwa e kitabo tebayawukanayawukana okutuusa nga obunnyonnyofu bumaze okubajjira
  98,5,"So nga ate tebaalagirwa okugyako okusinza Katonda yekka nga buli kyebakola bakikola ku lulwe yekka, awatali ku mugattirizaako kantu konna. Era nga bateekwa okuyimirizaawo e sswala n’okutoola Zzaka. Era nga eyo nno y'eddiini ennambulukufu"
  98,6,Mazima abo abaajeema mu bantu abaaweebwa e kitabo n’abo abagatta ku Katonda e bintu ebirala bakuyingira omuliro Jahannama mwe bagenda okubeera olubeerera. Abo nno be babi okusinga ebitonde ebirala byonna
  98,7,Mazima abo abakkiriza ne bakola e mirimu e mirungi be balungi okusinga ebitonde byonna
  98,8,"E mpeera yaabwe ewa Katonda waabwe kubayingiza jjana eyitibwa Aden, nga emigga gikulukutira mu yo. Baakugibeeramu olubeerera. Katonda yabasiima nabo ne bamusiima. Ebyo nno bigenda kufunwa oyo eyatya omuleziwe (Katonda)"
  99,1,E nsi bweriba eyuguumizziddwa oluyuguuma lwayo
  99,2,E nsi n'efulumya (nga ewandula) ebyo byonna ebigirimu
  99,3,Omuntu aligamba nga yeebuuza nti! ebadde ki
  99,4,Ku lunaku olwo egenda kuttottola ebigambo byonna ebikwata ku ebyo ebyakolerwanga ku yo
  99,5,Nti mazima Katonda y'aliba agiragidde okwogera ebyo
  99,6,Abantu ku lunaku olwo baliva mu kabbuli zaabwe nga bali mu bibinja babe nga balagibwa e mirimu gyabwe
  99,7,Omuntu eyakola omulimu omulungi gwonna kagube mutono gutya agenda kugulaba
  99,8,N'omuntu eyakola omulimu omubi gwonna kagube mutono gutya agenda kugulaba
  100,1,Ndayira embalaasi ezizinda(ezidduka) nga ziweevuuma
  100,2,Nezimansula e nsasi z’omuliroolw’okukoona enjazi
  100,3,Ezizinda ku maliiri
  100,4,"Nezisiikuula enfuufu, mu kutyekuula emisinde okwo"
  100,5,Neziyingira mu balabe wakati
  100,6,Mazima ddala omuntu mutomi eri omuleziwe
  100,7,Era mazima ye (omuntu) ku ky'obutomi mujulizi
  100,8,Era mazima yye muyitirivu nnyo mu kwagala ebyenfuna
  100,9,Abaffe (omuntu) tamanyi nti ebiri mu kabbuli bwe biriba bizuukiziddwa
  100,10,N’ebiri mu bifuba ne byolesebwa
  100,11,Mazima Katonda omulezi waabwe (nga bulijjo ne) ku lunaku olwo agenda kuba ng'amanyi byonna ebibakwatako
  101,1,Ekikoona (ekyentiisa)
  101,2,Ekikoona kye ki
  101,3,Naye omanyi ekikoona kye ki
  101,4,Lwe lunaku abantu lwe balibeera nga e biwojjolo ebisaasaanye
  101,5,N’ensozi lwe zirifuuka nga pamba omusuunsule afuumuuka
  101,6,"Naye, omuntu alibeera n'emirimu e mirungi nga gizitowa (okusinga ebibibye)"
  101,7,Oyo agenda kubeera mu bulamu obw’okwesiima
  101,8,Ate oyo aliwewukirwa emirimu gye emirungi (ebibi bye n’ebisinga obuzito)
  101,9,"Oyo nno, obuddo n'obutuulo bwe muliro oguyitibwa “Haawiya”"
  101,10,Naye omanyi ‘Haawiya’ kye ki
  101,11,Gwe muliro ogwengeredde (ogwokya ennyo)
  102,1,"Okunoonya okufuna ebingi, kubalabankanyizza (ne kubajja ku kugondera amateeka ga Katonda)"
  102,2,Okutuusa lwe muyingira kabbuli
  102,3,"Nedda, kyaddaki mujja kumanya (mu kiseera ky'okufa)"
  102,4,"Ate era oluvanyuma, kyaddaki mujja kumanya (nga muyingidde kabbuli)"
  102,5,"Nedda, singa nga mubadde mumanyi mu bukakafu bw'okumanya (temwandirabankanyiziddwa na kukungaanya bingi)"
  102,6,Mujja kulabira ddala omuliro “Jahiim”
  102,7,Ate oluvanyuma omuliro ogwo mujja kugulaba mugutegeerere ddala
  102,8,"Ate ddala oluvanyuma mugenda kubuuzibwa e byengera bye mwafuna ku nsi (mwabifuna mu makubo ki, era mwabisaasaanya mu makubo ki)"
  103,1,Ndayira omulembe (buli mulembe)
  103,2,Mazima ddala omuntu yenna gy’afa yenkana ali mu kufaafaaganirwa
  103,3,"Okugyako abo abakkiriza Katonda (mu nzikiriza entuufu) ate ne bakola e mirimu emirungi, era ne balaamirigana okukoleranga ku mazima (mu bulamu bwabwe bwonna) era ne balaamiragana okubeera abagumikiriza (mu bulamu bwabwe bwonna)"
  104,1,"Okubonaabona okwamaanyi kugenda kubeera ku buli muntu atambuza engambo, ageya banne n'abaggya obumogo"
  104,2,Oyo akungaanya ebyo bugagga n’abituuma
  104,3,Alowooza nti eby'obugaggabye byakumukuumira ku nsi obugenderevu
  104,4,"Nedda, ajja kukanyugwa mu muliro oguyitibwa “Hutwama”"
  104,5,Ye omanyi “Hutwama” kye ki
  104,6,"(Hutwama) muliro gwa Katonda omukume, ogubumbujja"
  104,7,Ogwo ogwokya negutuukira ddala ku mitima
  104,8,Mazima ddala omuliro ogwo (Hutwama) ku bantu abo (abogeddwaako) gugenda kubabuutikira
  104,9,Mu midumu emiwanvu
  105,1,Tewamanya Katonda kyeyakola eggye ly’enjovu
  105,2,Enkwe zaabwe tezaagwa butaka
  105,3,N'abasindikira e binnyonyi nga bijjira mu bibinja
  105,4,Nga bibakanyugira amayinja amookye
  105,5,Nebafuuka nga omuddo ogagayiddwa ensolo ne gufuluma nga gufuuse obusa
  106,1,Ku lw'empangaala ya ba Kuraish
  106,2,Empangaala yaabwe eyalimu okutambula engendo mu butiti ne mu kyeya
  106,3,Bateekwa basinze Katonda nannyini nyumba eno (Kaaba)
  106,4,"Katonda eyabawa eby'okulya, n’abawonya enjala, n’abawa e mirembe, ne bataba mu kutya"
  107,1,Olabye oyo alimbisa olunaku lw'enkomerero
  107,2,Oyo nno y’oyo awalagganya ba mulekwa
  107,3,Era nga takubiriza kuliisa banaku
  107,4,Okubonaabona kuli ku abo abasaala
  107,5,Nga balagajjalira e sswala zaabwe
  107,6,Abo abakola bandabe
  107,7,Era abamma bannaabwe ebintu ebitasaana kumma
  108,1,"Mazima ffe twakuwa e birungi e bingi, (mu ebyo mwe muli n'oluzzi Kauthara olw'omu jjana)"
  108,2,"N'olwekyo wenywereze ku kusaala ku lwa Katondawo, era osale n’ebisolo, nga osaddaaka ku lwa Katondawo"
  108,3,"Mazima oyo akuwalagganya, (ng'akuvuma era n'okukujeeja) ye wenkuggu"
  109,1,"Bagambe nti, abange mmwe abatakkiriza (abawakanyi)"
  109,2,"Ssisinza ebyo bye musinza (amasanamu, lubaale, n'ebirala)"
  109,3,Wadde namwe temusinza oyo gwe nsinza (ali omu mu bwa Katonda bwe)
  109,4,Era siri waakusinza ebyo bye musinza
  109,5,Era nammwe temuli baakusinza oyo gwensinza
  109,6,"Mulina e nkola yammwe (ey'okusinza ba Katonda abangi, nange nnina enkola yange (ey'okusinza Katonda omu yekka)"
  110,1,Okutaasa kwa Katonda n’obuwanguzi bwe bijjanga
  110,2,N’olaba abantu nga bayingira e ddiini ya Katonda mu bibinja
  110,3,"Otenderezanga Mukama Katondawo n’ebitendobye, era omwetondere, mazima yye akkiriza okwenenya"
  111,1,"Mu Hadith eri mu kitabo kya Bukhari Nabbi yagenda ku Batwhahu naakuba wuuli abantu bangi bajja nga balowooza nti waliyo ebya maguzi, Nabbi bweyatandika okubabuulira ebikwata ku Katonda, Abu Lahbi naakasuka e mikono nga bwagamba nti kino kyotukunganyirizza era kyotuyitidde? Zikirira. Katonda kwe kumwanukula mu ssura eno naagamba nti: (Gizikirire e mikono gya Abu Lahbi (gyawuuba), era ddala yenna yazikirira"
  111,2,"Eby'obugaggabwe tebimugasizza, wadde n’ebirala bye yafuna, (nga e kitiibwa)"
  111,3,Ajja kwesonseka mu muliro ogubumbujja
  111,4,Ne mukyalawe omwetissi w’enku (naye bwatyo)
  111,5,Nga mu nsingoye mulimu omuguwa omulange
  112,1,(Gwe Nabbi Muhammad) bagambe nti Katonda ali omu mu bwa Katondabwe (era nga yye yekka ateekeddwa okusinzibwa)
  112,2,Katonda y'akola ku byetaago by'ebitonde byonna
  112,3,"Tazaala, era teyazaalibwa"
  112,4,Era teri kintu kyonna kimwenkana
  113,1,"Gamba nti, nsaba obukuumi ewa Katonda afuga okukya kw’obudde"
  113,2,Mu bubi bw’ebyo bye yatonda
  113,3,Ne mu bubi bw’ekiro nga kikutte
  113,4,Ne mu bubi bw’abakazi abalogo abasiba ebifundikwa (ne babifuuwamu nga balaamiriza)
  113,5,Ne mu bubi obuva mu mukozi wensaalwa ng'akoze ensaalwa
  114,1,"Gamba nti, nsaba obukuumi okuva eri Mukama omulabirizi wa bantu"
  114,2,Omufuzi w'abantu
  114,3,Asinzibwa abantu
  114,4,Amponye obubi bw’omulabankanya sitaani omwekwesi
  114,5,Oyo alabankanya (e mitima egiri) mu bifuba by'abantu
  114,6,(Sitaani) ow’omu majiinni ne sitaani ow’omu bantu